# SD WebUI Repository Architecture Standards - UNIFIED SINGLE-CELL APPROACH

## 🏛️ FUNDAMENTAL ARCHITECTURE PRINCIPLES

### Notebook Structure (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
- **SINGLE CELL ARCHITECTURE** - One cell launches everything
- **Streamlit Middle Layer** - All operations through unified interface
- **No Cell Dependencies** - No need to run cells in sequence
- **Real-time State Management** - Streamlit handles all persistence
- **Enterprise backend with unified frontend**

### Required Single-Cell Structure
```python
#@title 🚀 Launch SD-DarkMaster-Pro Unified Interface
# Single cell that:
# 1. Detects platform and clones repository
# 2. Installs requirements
# 3. Launches Streamlit unified app
# 4. Creates public tunnel
# 5. Provides access URL
```

